The download scripts download several test data sets into the 
rsmas_insar/samples directory for quick testing.
#########################################
#### Quick testing ######################
#########################################
TESTBENCH                                 # alias to set $SCRATCHDIR 
make WellsquakeT399EnvD2.template
make ChamanT256F585EnvA.template
make SinabungT495F50AlosA.template
make CotopaxiT119TsxA.template 
make CotopaxiT58CskD.template
make PopoT263Rsat2HHD.template 
make KilaueaSM3T89F380Alos2A.template 
make KirishimaT79F247Jers.template
#########################################
#### Check the results ##################
#########################################
to look at the generated interferograms, go to $SCRATCHDIR and then 
look for the following files (I use the alias ff for find) and look at them using display
